    <lb n="11"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὥσ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>᾽ ἐμὲ τὸν <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἀ</supplied>δελ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">φ</supplied>ὸν αὐτοῦ Σιλβανὸν κατ᾽ εὐσεβίαν τοῦτον τὸν πα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῖ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">δ</supplied>α <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἔ</unclear>χειν 

